    "texte_orig": "Want[SP]the[SP]lowdown[SP]on[SP]rumors?\n[E1][E2][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Chief[SP]Todoroki\nAsk[SP]me[SP]to[SP]spread[SP]a[SP]rumor[SP]of[SP]your[SP]choice[SP]and\nI'll[SP]do[SP]it.[SP]Not[SP]for[SP]free,[SP]mind[SP]you.\n[E1][E2][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Chief[SP]Todoroki\nYou'll[SP]need[SP]to[SP]bring[SP]me[SP]rumors[SP]you[SP]hear[SP]from\nrumormongers.\n[E1][E2][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Chief[SP]Todoroki\nThere[SP]are[SP]rumormongers[SP]everywhere[SP]in[SP]Sumaru.\nDig[SP]a[SP]little,[SP]and[SP]you'll[SP]find[SP]them.\n[E1][E2][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Chief[SP]Todoroki\nYou[SP]can[SP]remind[SP]yourself[SP]which[SP]rumors[SP]are\nalready[SP]circulating[SP]by[SP]asking[SP]me[SP]to[SP]check\nrumors.\n[E1][E2][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Chief[SP]Todoroki\nNot[SP]only[SP]can[SP]you[SP]remember[SP]which[SP]rumors[SP]I've\nbeen[SP]putting[SP]out[SP]there[SP]for[SP]you,[SP]you[SP]can[SP]see\nwhich[SP]ones[SP]demons[SP]are[SP]spreading.",
